result of the investigation into the recent attack on the Chinese
Embassy to Yugoslavia at an earlier date, a Chinese diplomat said
here Friday.
</P>
<P>
Liu Xiaoming, minister of the Chinese Embassy to the United
States, said the U.S. government should speed up the probe into
the raid on the Chinese embassy in Belgrade and make the result
public swiftly to meet all demands of the Chinese government. (US-
China-Demand)
</P>
