<HEADLINE> Three Chinese Footballers Fined for Night Outings </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
HANOI, May 22 (Xinhua) -- Three Chinese footballers were fined
and seriously warned for not-informing night outings before the
upcoming 2000 Sydney Olympics soccer competition Asian Zone
qualifiers, a chief of the China Olympics soccer team announced on
Saturday.
</P>
<P>
