involved an overseas investment of over 5 million U.S. dollars
each. And solely overseas-funded projects made up 18.3 percent of
the total.
</P>
<P>
More than 30,000 products in 15 categories have been featured
during the trade fair, which has attracted over 800 businessmen
from 373 companies in 42 countries and regions.
</P>
<P>
Hebei has held this kind of trade fair for 16 years. 
