decisive fifth set which Thailand won 15-10.
</P>
<P>
In other matches on Friday, LG Caltex Oil Corp of South Korea
beat Kazakhstan's Alma-Dinamo 3-1, while the Chinese Taipei upset
Toyobo's Orchis of Japan 3-2.
</P>
<P>
