and Myanmar.
</P>
<P>
Indonesia lost 2-4 to defending champion Thailand in a penalty
shootout in the 19th Games final here in 1997. In this year's
Games, which is held for the first time in Brunei Darussalam,
Indonesia is aiming for a gold medal.
