<HEADLINE> Weekly Diplomatic News Highlights (2) </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Foreign Minister Tang Jiaxuan, in a meeting with his Kyrgyzstan
counterpart Muratbek Sansyzbayevich Yimanaliyev on Thursday, said
an important aspect of China's foreign policy is developing long-
term and stable friendship with neighboring countries, and China
is ready to further develop relations with Kyrgyzstan in the 21st
century.
</P>
<P>
Yimanaliyev responded his country places importance on its
relations with China and he believes that bilateral ties will be
developed in the next century.
